<div id="outline-container-headline-2" class="outline-2">
<h2 id="headline-2">
Proposed Solution
</h2>
<div id="outline-text-headline-2" class="outline-text-2">
<p>The first part of the code provides for a function to list all proper divisors for a given integer <code class="verbatim">x</code>. </p>
<p>
The loop determines the divisors for numbers 220 to 10,000, calculates their sum and then checks if these numbers are amicable. </p>
